Class SessionTableModel

java.lang.Object

      vista.set.SessionTableModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.table.TableModel
public class SessionTableModel
extends javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel

This class displays the session information as a table by implementing the TableModel. The table columns are the parts of the pathname and the ordering can be shuffled.
